---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import RentHumanoidSection from '../../components/blocks/RentHumanoidSection.vue';
---

<Layout
  title="Unitree G1 Humanoid Robot"
  description="For California residents and guests, our partners offer an exciting chance to rent a humanoid robot, a new product spreading across the market."
  ogImage="/website_cover_unitree.webp"
  pageTitle="Unitree G1 Humanoid Robot"
>

  <p class="layout layout__content space-b-2 intro">Rent the cutting-edge humanoid robot for your research, programming, and entertainment projects.</p>

  <RentHumanoidSection client:only/>

  <article class="layout space-b-2">
    <div class="grid-3 unitree-prices">
      <section class="oldy">
        <div class="space-b unitree__price-info">
          <span>Hour</span>
          <h5>$200</h5>
        </div>
        <ul>
          <li class="space-b-05">Rent on site (Oakland, CA)</li>
          <li class="space-b-05">Suitable for short tasks</li>
          <li class="space-b-05">No engineering support included</li>
        </ul>
      </section>
      <section class="oldy">
        <div class="space-b unitree__price-info">
          <span>Day</span>
          <h5>$900</h5>
        </div>
        <ul>
          <li class="space-b-05">Rent on site (Oakland, CA)</li>
          <li class="space-b-05">Suitable for bigger tasks</li>
          <li class="space-b-05">Basic engineering support included</li>
        </ul>
      </section>
      <section class="oldy">
        <div class="space-b unitree__price-info">
          <span>Week+</span>
          <h5>On demand</h5>
        </div>
        <ul>
          <li class="space-b-05">Delivery to your location</li>
          <li class="space-b-05">Customized approach</li>
          <li class="space-b-05">Engineering support can be included</li>
        </ul>
      </section>
    </div>
  </article>

  <h2 class="layout title-lined"><span>Enter the new era</span></h2>

  <article class="layout layout__text space-b-2">
    <p>The G1 humanoid robot with its innovative features offers versatility for research, programming, and entertainment needs. The Unitree G1 includes a Power Control Dexterous Hand, enabling it to perform delicate tasks such as handling objects, pressing buttons, and carrying out other precise operations with various items.</p>
    <img src="/images/devices/unitree-g1/unitree-g1-dex3.webp" alt="Unitree Dex3-1 Power Control Dexterous Hand, Operate Everything"/>
  </article>

  <h2 class="layout title-lined space-b-2"><span>Tech specification</span></h2>
  <article class="layout layout__text space-b-2 unitree-specification">
    <ul class="align-center">
      <li>
        <b>Height, Width and Thickness（Stand）</b>
        <span>1320x450x200mm</span>
      </li>
      <li>
        <b>Height, Width and Thickness（Fold）</b>
        <span>690x450x300mm</span>
      </li>
      <li>
        <b>Weight (With Battery)</b>
        <span>About 35kg</span>
      </li>
      <li>
        <b>Arm Maximum Load</b>
        <span>About 2Kg</span>
      </li>
      <li>
        <b>Cooling System</b>
        <span>Local air cooling</span>
      </li>
      <li>
        <b>Smart Battery (Quick Release)</b>
        <span>9000mAh</span>
      </li>
      <li>
        <b>Charger</b>
        <span>54V 5A</span>
      </li>
      <li>
        <b>Battery Life</b>
        <span>About 2h</span>
      </li>
      <li>
        <b>Sensing Sensor</b>
        <span>Depth Camera+3D LiDAR</span>
      </li>
      <li>
        <b>5W Speaker</b>
      </li>
      <li>
        <b>WiFi 6 , Bluetooth 5.2</b>
      </li>
      <li>
        <b>Manual Controller</b>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </article>

</Layout>


<style>

  ul {
    list-style: none;
    margin: 0;
  }

  section.oldy {
    width: 100%;
  }

  .intro {
    font-size: calc(var(--base-font-size) * 1.2);
    line-height: 1.2;
    text-align: center;
    font-variation-settings: var(--font-flex-medium);
  }

  .unitree-prices {
    justify-items: center;
  }

  .unitree__price-info h5 {
    font-size: calc(var(--base-font-size) * 1.7);
    font-variation-settings: var(--font-flex-extrabold);
    line-height: 1;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .unitree__price-info span {
    font-size: calc(var(--base-font-size) * 0.8);
    font-variation-settings: var(--font-flex-bold);
  }

  .unitree-specification li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .unitree-specification li:not(:last-child) {
    margin-bottom: calc(var(--space) * 0.8);
  }
  
</style>